	* cong-dispspec-registry.c, cong-document.c, cong-menus.c, cong-editor-widget.c, cong-plugin.c, cong-span-text-editor.c, cong-test-view.c, cong-tree-view.c, cursor.c, dispspec.c, open.c, plugin-docbook.c

